Movie: Percy Jackson & the Olympians: The Lightning Thief
Review: They were out of their minds expecting this to be the next Harry Potter with the amount of sexual innuendo in it.
It had to be turned off at the second iteration of pit bull munching down on a set of balls.
“HE WAS THE BEST GUY AROUND! WHAT MURDA?”
It would have taken Kevin 2 hours to create that damn map of his house. Wasting extra time on the flair and bubble letters of it.
The only time in human history that one is comforted to hear a Rick and Morty impression.
Rare instance of a serious depiction of man vaporized by electricity.
Cumshotted the big lizard to death
